      • jgetItem

        public static <S,I extends Item<S>,T extends Configurations.ConfigType<T>> java.util.Optional<I> jgetItem(T sc,
                                                                                                          Key<S,I> key)
        jgetItem returns an Item as an Optional. The Optional is empty if the item is not present.
        Type Parameters:
        S - The Scala type of the value
        I - The item type assocated with the Scala type
        T - The type of the configuration sc
        Parameters:
        sc - The configuration to use to search for the item
        key - The key for the item to be located
        Returns:
        Optional item
